description: ABOARD AIR FORCE ONE — President Trump told reporters Saturday that negotiations for a ceasefire between Russia and Ukraine were “going fine,” but indicated there needs to be a resolution soon. “I think Ukraine-Russia might be going OK. title: Trump: Russia-Ukraine talks ‘going OK,’ but point at which ‘you have to put up or shut up’
